  "handle": "fe696110-f-body-ls1-ls2-lsx-ls9-lq9-turbo-headers-manifolds-exhaust-1-3-4-primaries-compatible-with-camaro-firebird-gto-cts-corvette",
  "description": "<div>\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Chevrolet Camaro 1998-2019</li>\n<li>Chevrolet Corvette 1998-2019</li>\n<li>Cadillac CTS 2004-2013</li>\n<li>Pontiac Firebird 1998-2002</li>\n<li>Pontiac GTO 2004-2006</li>\n<li>* Fits LS1, LS2, LSX, LS9, LQ9 LS Series Universal F BODY Turbo Headers</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance</li>\n<li>Shorty design for power gain from idle to mid-range RPM</li>\n<li>Fully mandrel bent tubes made of high quality 16-gauge 304 stainless steel</li>\n<li>Head flanges laser-cut from high quality 3/8-inch thick steel plates</li>\n<li>The flange is flattened by a hydraulic press for precise and leak free sealing</li>\n<li>All joints are golden color TIG brass style welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n<li>Flanges chrome plated for corrosion resistance</li>\n<li>Polished surface for extra protection against rusting</li>\n<li>Accessories in the photos are included</li>\n<li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Header Type: Turbo</li>\n<li>Primary Diameter: 1-3/4 in.</li>\n<li>Collector Diameter: 2-1/2 in.</li>\n<li>Head Flange Thickness: 3/8 in.</li>\n<li>Pipe Thickness: 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n<li>Material: 304 Stainless Steel</li>\n<li>Finish: Polished</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
